Title: Relates to designating a portion of the state highway system in the hamlet of Uniondale as Jomani "Jo-Jo" Wright Way
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the hamlet of Uniondale as Jomani "Jo-Jo" Wright Way.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system in the hamlet of Uniondale as Jomani "Jo-Jo" Wright Way
